what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Isolated filtered dimensions (date, store, customer_demographics) into separate CTEs to enable predicate pushdown, then joined them directly with the fact table. This reduces the fact table scan early by applying selective filters from small dimension hash tables.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
